        "content": "<p>andreiltd opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13408\">PR #13408</a> from <code>andreiltd:fix/http-concurrent-write</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Move the P3 HTTP fixture helper's request body write/drop path into the outer join with client::send and the transmit future.</p>\n<p>This avoids requiring client::send to complete before the request body producer is driven to eof, which can deadlock with servers that read the full request body before sending response headers.</p>\n<p>More details can be found in the zulip discussion: <a href=\"#narrow/channel/219900-wasi/topic/p3.20http.20helper.20and.20request.2Fresponse.20deadlock/with/595890351\">https://bytecodealliance.zulipchat.com/#narrow/channel/219900-wasi/topic/p3.20http.20helper.20and.20request.2Fresponse.20deadlock/with/595890351</a></p>\n</blockquote>",
